						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle">skrasms wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent"><div class="quotetitle">blargg wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">First off, your switch statement is missing breaks, so every one falls through. Second, is the microcontroller fast enough?</div><br /><br />Not sure how I forget every break statement, thanks for pointing that out. The micro is running at 40 Mhz right now, do I need it faster than that?</div>
