					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle"><b>Quote:</b></div><div class="quotecontent">But don't these microcontrollers already tend to have a DAC on them, to which one could feed values from 0 to 63?</div>
<br />Not that have non-linearity that affects the volume of the 2A03's triangle and noise channels. If one didn't care about the 2A03's quirks, one could do all the channels with a microcontroller alone.</div>

